Package: koala.nowcast
Title: KOALA Nowcast Pipeline for German Election Polls
Version: 0.1.0
Description:
    Automated nowcast pipeline for German federal and state elections.
    Scrapes poll data from wahlrecht.de, pools surveys using Bayesian
    methods, and computes Monte Carlo-based coalition probabilities and
    seat distributions via the coalitions package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    coalitions (>= 0.6.27),
    dplyr (>= 1.2.1),
    jsonlite (>= 2.0.0),
    tidyr,
    yaml (>= 2.3.10)
